****CudNN Install****

1. With downloaded .deb file :   sudo dpkg -i ???.deb

2. To check whether downloaded :  " cat /usr/local/cuda/include/cudnn_version.h | grep CUDNN_MAJOR -A 2 "
=> #define CUDNN_MAJOR 8
   #define CUDNN_MINOR 2 
   ...
   Then installed

